Package CADI.Common.Cache

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BinDescriptor
    Further information, see ISO/IEC 15444-9 sect.
    CacheManagement  
    CacheModel
    This class implements a basic cache model.
    DataBin
    This class is a container for JPEG2000 Data-bins.
    DataBinsCacheManagement
    This class implements some useful method for the maganement of a cache of data-bins.
    DataBinStream
    This class is designated to save an stream of bytes.
    ExplicitBinDescriptor
    This class is used as a container for the explicit-bin-descriptor.
    ImplicitBinDescriptor
    This class is used as a container for the implicit-bin-descriptor.
    MainHeaderDataBin
    Extends the DataBin class to Main header-based data (codestream main header).
    MetaDataBin
    Extends the DataBin class to Meta data-based data (codestream main header).
    ModelElement
    Further information, see ISO/IEC 15444-9 sect.
    PrecinctDataBin
    Extends the DataBin class to support precinct-based data bins.
    TileHeaderDataBin
    Extends the DataBin class to support Tile header-based data.
